    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible, 'like-new' shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s sparkling clean, runs perfectly, and is just waiting for someone new to love it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
