      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a superlative example of the E46 chassis, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Mated to a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, the drivetrain delivers a linear power band culminating in an 8,000 RPM redline. The suspension geometry remains taut, with verified subframe reinforcement and factory-spec bushings ensuring razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in a concours-level Carbon Black Metallic, this vehicle has been maintained to exacting standards, preserving the mechanical integrity and tactile feedback synonymous with BMW\u2019s peak atmospheric era. A true driver\u2019s specimen for the collector who demands uncompromised performance and structural perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
