    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman in pristine Guards Red. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the black leather interior retains its original matte finish and 'new car' scent, with no bolster wear or sun fading. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete binder of records included. With only 12,000 babied miles, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a showroom-quality example of a modern classic. Not a single scratch on the 20-inch Carrera S wheels, and the Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires are near-new. It runs perfectly, shifts smoothly, and needs absolutely nothing.",
      "price": 48500.0,
