      "description": "This E92 M3 is a concours-grade specimen featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. The power delivery is linear and visceral, breathing through eight individual throttle bodies and redlining at 8,400 RPM. This example remains in showroom condition with impeccable paint depth and a chassis free of any oxidation. Mechanically, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed preventatively, ensuring the structural integrity of the high-revving internals. The M-Variable differential and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) operate with factory precision, providing a telepathic connection between the Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber and the tarmac. No subframe fatigue, no fluid seepage\u2014just a pure mechanical symphony in a pristine wrapper.",
